                    <Property name="text" type="java.lang.String" value="BOND (Bridging Organizations and Networks for Discovery) is a centralized desktop-based system  &#xa;designed to organize and manage student organization information. It allows users to explore &#xa;organization profiles,  officer records, and events without requiring login. The system enhances&#xa;accessibility  and transparency by  providing a single, reliable platform for organizational data."/>
